    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Have you ever try to call it with `useCallback` ? According to React document `useCallback` will return a memoized version of the callback that only changes if one of the dependencies has changed. So It would be helpful for methods like `debounce`.\r\n\r\n```\r\nuseCallback(_.debounce(()=>......., 500), []);\r\n```",
